  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shape Raid is an online <strong>co-op</strong> <strong>boss rush</strong> game. Play alone or with up to 7 friends in this unique <strong>bullet hell</strong> experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The objective is simple. Choose your favorite shape -> Choose your ideal ability -> Fight bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-30 Unique Boss Battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-2 Distinct Game Modes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-3 Difficulty Options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-100+ Customization Options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Dozens of tasks to complete</p>",
